{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":986,"text":"On Mondays and Thursdays,\nI learn how to die."},{"time":5178,"text":"I call them my terminal days."},{"time":7102,"text":"My wife Fernanda doesn't like the term,"},{"time":9936,"text":"but a lot of people in my family died\nof melanoma cancer"},{"time":14738,"text":"and my parents and grandparents had it."},{"time":17373,"text":"And I kept thinking, one day I could\nbe sitting in front of a doctor"},{"time":20657,"text":"who looks at my exams and says,"},{"time":22779,"text":"\"Ricardo, things don't look very good."},{"time":25094,"text":"You have six months or a year to live.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":27773,"text":"And you start thinking about\nwhat you would do with this time."},{"time":31034,"text":"And you say, \"I'm going to spend \nmore time with the kids."},{"time":33839,"text":"I'm going to visit these places,"},{"time":35423,"text":"I'm going to go up and down\nmountains and places"},{"time":37916,"text":"and I'm going to do all the things\nI didn't do when I had the time.\""},{"time":41806,"text":"But of course, we all know"},{"time":43639,"text":"these are very bittersweet memories \nwe're going to have."},{"time":46623,"text":"It's very difficult to do."},{"time":47946,"text":"You spend a good part of the time\ncrying, probably."},{"time":51599,"text":"So I said, I'm going to do something else."}]},{"cues":[{"time":53986,"text":"Every Monday and Thursday,\nI'm going use my terminal days."},{"time":58825,"text":"And I will do, during those days,"},{"time":61194,"text":"whatever it is I was going to do\nif I had received that piece of news."},{"time":64721,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":66094,"text":"When you think about --"},{"time":68128,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":72293,"text":"when you think about the opposite of work,"},{"time":74770,"text":"we, many times, think it's leisure."},{"time":77247,"text":"And you say, ah, I need \nsome leisure time, and so forth."},{"time":80314,"text":"But the fact is that,\nleisure is a very busy thing."},{"time":83851,"text":"You go play golf and tennis,\nand you meet people,"},{"time":86250,"text":"and you're going for lunch,\nand you're late for the movies."},{"time":89362,"text":"It's a very crowded thing that we do."},{"time":91410,"text":"The opposite of work is idleness."},{"time":95530,"text":"But very few of us know\nwhat to do with idleness."},{"time":97945,"text":"When you look at the way\nthat we distribute our lives in general,"},{"time":102007,"text":"you realize that in the periods\nin which we have a lot of money,"},{"time":106561,"text":"we have very little time."},{"time":108558,"text":"And then when we finally have time,\nwe have neither the money nor the health."}]},{"cues":[{"time":113585,"text":"So we started thinking about that\nas a company for the last 30 years."},{"time":118205,"text":"This is a complicated company\nwith thousands of employees,"},{"time":121376,"text":"hundreds of millions\nof dollars of business"},{"time":123736,"text":"that makes rocket fuel propellent systems,\nruns 4,000 ATMs in Brazil,"},{"time":130289,"text":"does income tax preparation\nfor dozens of thousands."},{"time":133646,"text":"So this is not a simple business."}]},{"cues":[{"time":137258,"text":"We looked at it and we said,"},{"time":139386,"text":"let's devolve to these people,\nlet's give these people a company"},{"time":144254,"text":"where we take away\nall the boarding school aspects"},{"time":146634,"text":"of, this is when you arrive,\nthis is how you dress,"},{"time":149023,"text":"this is how you go to meetings,\nthis is what you say,"},{"time":151585,"text":"this is what you don't say,"},{"time":152906,"text":"and let's see what's left."},{"time":154412,"text":"So we started this about 30 years ago,"},{"time":156242,"text":"and we started dealing\nwith this very issue."},{"time":158767,"text":"And so we said, look, the retirement,"},{"time":160964,"text":"the whole issue of how \nwe distribute our graph of life."},{"time":164106,"text":"Instead of going mountain climbing\nwhen you're 82,"},{"time":167263,"text":"why don't you do it next week?"},{"time":169436,"text":"And we'll do it like this,"},{"time":170791,"text":"we'll sell you back your Wednesdays\nfor 10 percent of your salary."},{"time":175187,"text":"So now, if you were going to be \na violinist, which you probably weren't,"},{"time":179440,"text":"you go and do this on Wednesday."}]},{"cues":[{"time":181594,"text":"And what we found --"},{"time":182941,"text":"we thought, these are the older people"},{"time":185478,"text":"who are going to be really interested\nin this program."},{"time":188077,"text":"And the average age\nof the first people who adhered"},{"time":190531,"text":"were 29, of course."},{"time":191979,"text":"And so we started looking,"},{"time":193337,"text":"and we said, we have to do things\nin a different way."},{"time":195837,"text":"So we started saying things like,"},{"time":197608,"text":"why do we want to know\nwhat time you came to work,"},{"time":199982,"text":"what time you left, etc.?"},{"time":201233,"text":"Can't we exchange this for a contract"},{"time":203587,"text":"for buying something from you,\nsome kind of work?"},{"time":207049,"text":"Why are we building these headquarters?"},{"time":209070,"text":"Is it not an ego issue\nthat we want to look solid"},{"time":211838,"text":"and big and important?"},{"time":213717,"text":"But we're dragging you two hours\nacross town because of it?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":217001,"text":"So we started asking questions one by one."},{"time":220532,"text":"We'd say it like this:"},{"time":221925,"text":"One: How do we find people?"},{"time":224207,"text":"We'd go out and try\nand recruit people and we'd say,"},{"time":227390,"text":"look, when you come to us,"},{"time":228943,"text":"we're not going to have\ntwo or three interviews"},{"time":231165,"text":"and then you're going to be\nmarried to us for life."},{"time":233577,"text":"That's not how we do \nthe rest of our lives."},{"time":235727,"text":"So, come have your interviews."},{"time":237832,"text":"Anyone who's interested\nin interviewing, you will show up."},{"time":241268,"text":"And then we'll see what happens\nout of the intuition that rises from that,"},{"time":245261,"text":"instead of just filling out the little \nitems of whether you're the right person."},{"time":249303,"text":"And then, come back."},{"time":251420,"text":"Spend an afternoon, spend a whole day,\ntalk to anybody you want."},{"time":254481,"text":"Make sure we are the bride \nyou thought we were"},{"time":257542,"text":"and not all the bullshit\nwe put into our own ads."},{"time":260605,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":262681,"text":"Slowly we went to a process \nwhere we'd say things like,"},{"time":266377,"text":"we don't want anyone to be\na leader in the company"},{"time":269138,"text":"if they haven't been \ninterviewed and approved"},{"time":271281,"text":"by their future subordinates."},{"time":274132,"text":"Every six months, everyone gets \nevaluated, anonymously, as a leader."},{"time":279588,"text":"And this determines whether they should\ncontinue in that leadership position,"},{"time":283620,"text":"which is many times\nsituational, as you know."},{"time":286410,"text":"And so if they don't have 70, 80 percent \nof a grade, they don't stay,"},{"time":292464,"text":"which is probably the reason why\nI haven't been CEO for more than 10 years."},{"time":296803,"text":"And over time, we started asking\nother questions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":300699,"text":"We said things like,"},{"time":302215,"text":"why can't people set their own salaries?"},{"time":305544,"text":"What do they need to know?"},{"time":307120,"text":"There's only three things \nyou need to know:"},{"time":309183,"text":"how much people make inside the company,"},{"time":311518,"text":"how much people make somewhere\nelse in a similar business"},{"time":314387,"text":"and how much we make in general\nto see whether we can afford it."},{"time":317679,"text":"So let's give people these three\npieces of information."},{"time":320264,"text":"So we started having, in the cafeteria,"},{"time":322272,"text":"a computer where you could go in \nand you could ask"},{"time":324773,"text":"what someone spent, \nhow much someone makes,"},{"time":326970,"text":"what they make in benefits, \nwhat the company makes,"},{"time":329450,"text":"what the margins are, and so forth."},{"time":331760,"text":"And this is 25 years ago."}]},{"cues":[{"time":335452,"text":"As this information started \ncoming to people,"},{"time":338187,"text":"we said things like, we don't want \nto see your expense report,"},{"time":341296,"text":"we don't want to know how many \nholidays you're taking,"},{"time":343892,"text":"we don't want to know where you work."},{"time":345780,"text":"We had, at one point,\n14 different offices around town,"},{"time":348756,"text":"and we'd say, go to the one \nthat's closest to your house,"},{"time":352150,"text":"to the customer that \nyou're going to visit today."},{"time":354651,"text":"Don't tell us where you are."},{"time":356770,"text":"And more, even when we had\nthousands of people, 5,000 people,"},{"time":360895,"text":"we had two people in the H.R. department,"},{"time":364273,"text":"and thankfully one of them has retired."},{"time":366671,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":368630,"text":"And so, the question we were asking was,\nhow can we be taking care of people?"},{"time":372384,"text":"People are the only thing we have."},{"time":374187,"text":"We can't have a department that runs\nafter people and looks after people."},{"time":377625,"text":"So as we started finding that this worked,\nand we'd say, we're looking for --"},{"time":383006,"text":"and this is, I think,\nthe main thing I was looking for"},{"time":385701,"text":"in the terminal days and in the company,"},{"time":387744,"text":"which is, how do you set up for wisdom?"},{"time":391313,"text":"We've come from an age of revolution,\nindustrial revolution,"},{"time":395989,"text":"an age of information,\nan age of knowledge,"},{"time":398672,"text":"but we're not any closer\nto the age of wisdom."},{"time":401284,"text":"How we design, how do we organize,\nfor more wisdom?"},{"time":404611,"text":"So for example, many times,"},{"time":406154,"text":"what's the smartest or the intelligent\ndecision doesn't jive."},{"time":410501,"text":"So we'd say things like,"},{"time":412883,"text":"let's agree that you're going to sell\n57 widgets per week."},{"time":416890,"text":"If you sell them by Wednesday, \nplease go to the beach."},{"time":420563,"text":"Don't create a problem for us, \nfor manufacturing, for application,"},{"time":424274,"text":"then we have to buy new companies,\nwe have to buy our competitors,"},{"time":427377,"text":"we have to do all kinds of things\nbecause you sold too many widgets."},{"time":430599,"text":"So go to the beach\nand start again on Monday."},{"time":432835,"text":"(Laughter) (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":435271,"text":"So the process is looking for wisdom."},{"time":438610,"text":"And in the process, of course, \nwe wanted people to know everything,"},{"time":442150,"text":"and we wanted to be truly democratic\nabout the way we ran things."},{"time":445519,"text":"So our board had two seats open \nwith the same voting rights,"},{"time":451210,"text":"for the first two people who showed up."},{"time":453328,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":454896,"text":"And so we had cleaning ladies voting\non a board meeting,"},{"time":460132,"text":"which had a lot of other very important\npeople in suits and ties."},{"time":463228,"text":"And the fact is that they kept us honest."}]},{"cues":[{"time":466857,"text":"This process, as we started looking\nat the people who came to us,"},{"time":470606,"text":"we'd say, now wait a second,"},{"time":472184,"text":"people come to us and they say,\nwhere am I supposed to sit?"},{"time":475067,"text":"How am I supposed to work?\nWhere am I going to be in 5 years' time?"},{"time":478308,"text":"And we looked at that and we said,\nwe have to start much earlier."},{"time":481386,"text":"Where do we start?"},{"time":482409,"text":"We said, oh, kindergarten \nseems like a good place."}]},{"cues":[{"time":484924,"text":"So we set up a foundation, which now has, \nfor 11 years, three schools,"},{"time":489581,"text":"where we started asking\nthe same questions,"},{"time":491883,"text":"how do you redesign school for wisdom?"},{"time":494795,"text":"It is one thing to say,\nwe need to recycle the teachers,"},{"time":497724,"text":"we need the directors to do more."},{"time":499401,"text":"But the fact is that what we do\nwith education is entirely obsolete."},{"time":505333,"text":"The teacher's role is entirely obsolete."},{"time":507831,"text":"Going from a math class, to biology,\nto 14th-century France is very silly."},{"time":513482,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":518184,"text":"So we started thinking, \nwhat could it look like?"},{"time":520913,"text":"And we put together people, \nincluding people who like education,"},{"time":524482,"text":"people like Paulo Freire, \nand two ministers of education in Brazil"},{"time":529917,"text":"and we said, if we were to design\na school from scratch,"},{"time":532586,"text":"what would it look like?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":534013,"text":"And so we created this school,\nwhich is called Lumiar,"},{"time":537746,"text":"and Lumiar, one of them\nis a public school,"},{"time":539898,"text":"and Lumiar says the following:"},{"time":541704,"text":"Let's divide this role\nof the teacher into two."},{"time":545881,"text":"One guy, we'll call a tutor."},{"time":548242,"text":"A tutor, in the old sense of the Greek\n\"paideia\": Look after the kid."},{"time":553217,"text":"What's happening at home,\nwhat's their moment in life, etc.."},{"time":557047,"text":"But please don't teach,"},{"time":558387,"text":"because the little you know compared \nto Google, we don't want to know."},{"time":561797,"text":"Keep that to yourself."},{"time":562949,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":564297,"text":"Now, we'll bring in people\nwho have two things:"},{"time":568250,"text":"passion and expertise, and it could be\ntheir profession or not."},{"time":572617,"text":"And we use the senior citizens,"},{"time":574534,"text":"who are 25 percent of the population\nwith wisdom that nobody wants anymore."},{"time":578887,"text":"So we bring them to school and we say,"},{"time":581494,"text":"teach these kids whatever\nyou really believe in."},{"time":585330,"text":"So we have violinists teaching math."},{"time":587946,"text":"We have all kinds of things where we say,"},{"time":590511,"text":"don't worry about \nthe course material anymore."},{"time":593492,"text":"We have approximately 10 great threads\nthat go from 2 to 17."},{"time":598456,"text":"Things like, how do we measure\nourselves as humans?"},{"time":602846,"text":"So there's a place for math and physics\nand all that there."},{"time":606472,"text":"How do we express ourselves?"},{"time":608336,"text":"So there's a place\nfor music and literature, etc.,"},{"time":610741,"text":"but also for grammar."}]},{"cues":[{"time":612385,"text":"And then we have things\nthat everyone has forgotten,"},{"time":615042,"text":"which are probably the most \nimportant things in life."},{"time":617611,"text":"The very important things in life,\nwe know nothing about."},{"time":621309,"text":"We know nothing about love,"},{"time":623549,"text":"we know nothing about death,"},{"time":625641,"text":"we know nothing about why we're here."},{"time":627718,"text":"So we need a thread in school that\ntalks about everything we don't know."},{"time":632252,"text":"So that's a big part of what we do."},{"time":634356,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":639951,"text":"So over the years, we started going\ninto other things."},{"time":642869,"text":"We'd say, why do we have to scold the kids"},{"time":645031,"text":"and say, sit down and come here \nand do that, and so forth."},{"time":647822,"text":"We said, let's get the kids to do \nsomething we call a circle,"},{"time":651137,"text":"which meets once a week."},{"time":652402,"text":"And we'd say, you put the rules together"},{"time":654712,"text":"and then you decide\nwhat you want to do with it."},{"time":657039,"text":"So can you all hit yourself on the head?"},{"time":659221,"text":"Sure, for a week, try."},{"time":661543,"text":"They came up with the very same\nrules that we had,"},{"time":665478,"text":"except they're theirs."},{"time":666869,"text":"And then, they have the power,"},{"time":669114,"text":"which means, they can and do\nsuspend and expel kids"},{"time":674106,"text":"so that we're not playing school,\nthey really decide."}]},{"cues":[{"time":679504,"text":"And then, in this same vein,"},{"time":682547,"text":"we keep a digital mosaic,"},{"time":684941,"text":"because this is not constructivist\nor Montessori or something."},{"time":688572,"text":"It's something where we keep\nthe Brazilian curriculum"},{"time":692110,"text":"with 600 tiles of a mosaic,"},{"time":694778,"text":"which we want to expose these kids\nto by the time they're 17."},{"time":697915,"text":"And follow this all the time\nand we know how they're doing"},{"time":700750,"text":"and we say, you're not interested \nin this now, let's wait a year."},{"time":704804,"text":"And the kids are in groups\nthat don't have an age category,"},{"time":709036,"text":"so the six-year-old kid\nwho is ready for that with an 11-year-old,"},{"time":712762,"text":"that eliminates all of the gangs\nand the groups"},{"time":715127,"text":"and this stuff that we have \nin the schools, in general."},{"time":719012,"text":"And they have a zero \nto 100 percent grading,"},{"time":721453,"text":"which they do themselves with an app\nevery couple of hours."},{"time":725254,"text":"Until we know they're 37 percent of the\nway we'd like them to be on this issue,"},{"time":729689,"text":"so that we can send them out in the world\nwith them knowing enough about it."},{"time":734584,"text":"And so the courses are World Cup Soccer,\nor building a bicycle."},{"time":739827,"text":"And people will sign up for \na 45-day course on building a bicycle."},{"time":744098,"text":"Now, try to build a bicycle without \nknowing that pi is 3.1416."},{"time":748667,"text":"You can't."},{"time":750431,"text":"And try, any one of you, \nusing 3.1416 for something."},{"time":755083,"text":"You don't know anymore."},{"time":756589,"text":"So this is lost and that's what \nwe try to do there,"},{"time":759020,"text":"which is looking \nfor wisdom in that school."}]},{"cues":[{"time":761134,"text":"And that brings us back to this graph\nand this distribution of our life."},{"time":767090,"text":"I accumulated a lot of money \nwhen I think about it."},{"time":769751,"text":"When you think and you say,\nnow is the time to give back --"},{"time":773998,"text":"well, if you're giving back, \nyou took too much."},{"time":776670,"text":"(Laughter) (Applause)"},{"time":784822,"text":"I keep thinking of Warren Buffet\nwaking up one day"},{"time":787402,"text":"and finding out he has 30 billion dollars\nmore than he thought he had."},{"time":790786,"text":"And he looks and he says,\nwhat am I going to do with this?"},{"time":793578,"text":"And he says, I'll give it to someone\nwho really needs this."},{"time":796415,"text":"I'll give it to Bill Gates. (Laughter)"},{"time":800086,"text":"And my guy, who's my financial\nadvisor in New York,"},{"time":803236,"text":"he says, look, you're a silly guy"},{"time":805129,"text":"because you would have 4.1 times \nmore money today"},{"time":808402,"text":"if you had made money with money\ninstead of sharing as you go."},{"time":812668,"text":"But I like sharing as you go better."},{"time":814480,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":817786,"text":"I taught MBAs at MIT for a time"},{"time":822058,"text":"and I ended up, one day,\nat the Mount Auburn Cemetery."},{"time":824664,"text":"It is a beautiful cemetery in Cambridge."},{"time":826608,"text":"And I was walking around.\nIt was my birthday and I was thinking."},{"time":829650,"text":"And the first time around, \nI saw these tombstones"},{"time":832044,"text":"and these wonderful people \nwho'd done great things"},{"time":834817,"text":"and I thought, what do I want \nto be remembered for?"},{"time":838889,"text":"And I did another stroll around,"},{"time":840485,"text":"and the second time,\nanother question came to me,"},{"time":842930,"text":"which did me better, which was,"},{"time":845233,"text":"why do I want to be remembered at all?"},{"time":848120,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":850257,"text":"And that, I think, \ntook me different places."},{"time":853078,"text":"When I was 50, my wife Fernanda and I\nsat for a whole afternoon,"},{"time":857326,"text":"we had a big pit with fire,"},{"time":859508,"text":"and I threw everything I had ever \ndone into that fire."},{"time":863084,"text":"This is a book in 38 languages,"},{"time":865471,"text":"hundreds and hundreds of articles\nand DVDs, everything there was."},{"time":869018,"text":"And that did two things."},{"time":870438,"text":"One, it freed our five kids\nfrom following in our steps, our shadow --"},{"time":875363,"text":"They don't know what I do."},{"time":877019,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":878243,"text":"Which is good."},{"time":879552,"text":"And I'm not going to take them somewhere"},{"time":881477,"text":"and say, one day \nall of this will be yours."},{"time":883871,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":885428,"text":"The five kids know nothing, which is good."}]},{"cues":[{"time":888960,"text":"And the second thing is,"},{"time":890641,"text":"I freed myself from this anchor\nof past achievement or whatever."},{"time":895339,"text":"I'm free to start something new every time\nand to decide things from scratch"},{"time":899837,"text":"in part of those terminal days."},{"time":901958,"text":"And some people would say,"},{"time":903375,"text":"oh, so now you have this time,\nthese terminal days,"},{"time":905913,"text":"and so you go out and do everything."},{"time":907771,"text":"No, we've been to the beaches,"},{"time":910093,"text":"so we've been to Samoa and Maldives\nand Mozambique,"},{"time":912655,"text":"so that's done."},{"time":914421,"text":"I've climbed mountains in the Himalayas."},{"time":916530,"text":"I've gone down 60 meters to see \nhammerhead sharks."},{"time":920401,"text":"I've spent 59 days on the back of a camel\nfrom Chad to Timbuktu."},{"time":924952,"text":"I've gone to the magnetic \nNorth Pole on a dog sled."},{"time":928943,"text":"So, we've been busy."},{"time":930719,"text":"It's what I'd like to call \nmy empty bucket list."},{"time":936722,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":939701,"text":"And with this rationale,\nI look at these days and I think,"},{"time":943258,"text":"I'm not retired. \nI don't feel retired at all."},{"time":945777,"text":"And so I'm writing a new book."},{"time":947918,"text":"We started three new companies\nin the last two years."},{"time":951731,"text":"I'm now working on getting this \nschool system for free out into the world,"},{"time":956934,"text":"and I've found, very interestingly enough,\nthat nobody wants it for free."},{"time":960387,"text":"And so I've been trying for 10 years"},{"time":962325,"text":"to get the public system\nto take over this school rationale,"},{"time":965750,"text":"much as the public schools we have,"},{"time":968145,"text":"which has instead of 43 out of 100,\nas their rating, as their grades,"},{"time":972842,"text":"has 91 out of 100."},{"time":975531,"text":"But for free, nobody wants it."},{"time":977964,"text":"So maybe we'll start charging for it \nand then it will go somewhere."},{"time":981158,"text":"But getting this out is one\nof the things we want to do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":984939,"text":"And I think what this leaves us\nas a message for all of you,"},{"time":988256,"text":"I think is a little bit like this:"},{"time":990008,"text":"We've all learned\nhow to go on Sunday night"},{"time":993165,"text":"to email and work from home."},{"time":995582,"text":"But very few of us have learned"},{"time":997292,"text":"how to go to the movies\non Monday afternoon."},{"time":1000422,"text":"And if we're looking for wisdom,\nwe need to learn to do that as well."},{"time":1004523,"text":"And so, what we've done all\nof these years is very simple,"},{"time":1008173,"text":"is use the little tool,\nwhich is ask three whys in a row."},{"time":1011345,"text":"Because the first why\nyou always have a good answer for."},{"time":1014106,"text":"The second why,\nit starts getting difficult."},{"time":1016521,"text":"By the third why, you don't really know\nwhy you're doing what you're doing."},{"time":1020460,"text":"What I want to leave you with is the seed\nand the thought that maybe if you do this,"},{"time":1026688,"text":"you will come to the question, what for?"},{"time":1029444,"text":"What am I doing this for?"},{"time":1030946,"text":"And hopefully, as a result of that,\nand over time,"},{"time":1033827,"text":"I hope that with this,\nand that's what I'm wishing you,"},{"time":1036960,"text":"you'll have a much wiser future."},{"time":1039663,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":1041448,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1053957,"text":"Chris Anderson: So Ricardo, \nyou're kind of crazy."},{"time":1059044,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":1060869,"text":"To many people, this seems crazy."},{"time":1064049,"text":"And yet so deeply wise, also."},{"time":1067438,"text":"The pieces I'm trying\nto put together are this:"},{"time":1070347,"text":"Your ideas are so radical."},{"time":1072442,"text":"How, in business, for example,\nthese ideas have been out for a while,"},{"time":1078191,"text":"probably the percentage of businesses \nthat have taken some of them"},{"time":1081401,"text":"is still quite low."},{"time":1083303,"text":"Are there any times you've seen \nsome big company"},{"time":1086201,"text":"take on one of your ideas \nand you've gone, \"Yes!\"?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1089830,"text":"Ricardo Semler: It happens.\nIt happened about two weeks ago"},{"time":1092627,"text":"with Richard Branson,\nwith his people saying,"},{"time":1094837,"text":"oh, I don't want to control\nyour holidays anymore,"},{"time":1097369,"text":"or Netflix does a little bit\nof this and that,"},{"time":1099553,"text":"but I don't think it's very important."},{"time":1101880,"text":"I'd like to see it happen maybe a little\nbit in a bit of a missionary zeal,"},{"time":1105634,"text":"but that's a very personal one."},{"time":1107208,"text":"But the fact is that it takes a leap \nof faith about losing control."},{"time":1111420,"text":"And almost nobody who is in control\nis ready to take leaps of faith."},{"time":1114716,"text":"It will have to come from kids \nand other people"},{"time":1117056,"text":"who are starting companies \nin a different way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1119298,"text":"CA: So that's the key thing?"},{"time":1120806,"text":"From your point of view\nthe evidence is there,"},{"time":1123005,"text":"in the business point of view this works,"},{"time":1125001,"text":"but people just don't have\nthe courage to -- (Whoosh)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1127709,"text":"RS: They don't even have the incentive."},{"time":1129831,"text":"You're running a company\nwith a 90-day mandate."},{"time":1132587,"text":"It's a quarterly report."},{"time":1134466,"text":"If you're not good in 90 days, you're out."},{"time":1136684,"text":"So you say, \"Here's a great program that,\nin less than one generation --\""},{"time":1140605,"text":"And the guy says, \"Get out of here.\""},{"time":1142529,"text":"So this is the problem."},{"time":1144420,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1147335,"text":"CA: What you're trying to do in education\nseems to me incredibly profound."},{"time":1152651,"text":"Everyone is bothered about\ntheir country's education system."},{"time":1157149,"text":"No one thinks that\nwe've caught up yet to a world"},{"time":1159922,"text":"where there's Google and all these \ntechnological options."},{"time":1162872,"text":"So you've got actual evidence now that \nthe kids so far going through your system,"},{"time":1166742,"text":"there's a dramatic increase \nin performance."},{"time":1169294,"text":"How do we help you move\nthese ideas forward?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1171859,"text":"RS: I think it's that problem\nof ideas whose time has come."},{"time":1176750,"text":"And I've never been very evangelical\nabout these things."},{"time":1180252,"text":"We put it out there."},{"time":1181793,"text":"Suddenly, you find people --"},{"time":1183238,"text":"there's a group in Japan, \nwhich scares me very much,"},{"time":1185753,"text":"which is called the Semlerists,\nand they have 120 companies."},{"time":1188918,"text":"They've invited me.\nI've always been scared to go."},{"time":1193289,"text":"And there is a group in Holland\nthat has 600 small, Dutch companies."},{"time":1198464,"text":"It's something that\nwill flourish on its own."},{"time":1201141,"text":"Part of it will be wrong, \nand it doesn't matter."},{"time":1203632,"text":"This will find its own place."},{"time":1205709,"text":"And I'm afraid\nof the other one, which says,"},{"time":1208194,"text":"this is so good you've got to do this."},{"time":1210126,"text":"Let's set up a system \nand put lots of money into it"},{"time":1212792,"text":"and then people will do it no matter what."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1215319,"text":"CA: So you have asked \nextraordinary questions your whole life."},{"time":1218563,"text":"It seems to me that's the fuel \nthat's driven a lot of this."},{"time":1221396,"text":"Do you have any other questions for us,\nfor TED, for this group here?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1227265,"text":"RS: I always come back \nto variations of the question"},{"time":1231854,"text":"that my son asked me when he was three."},{"time":1235105,"text":"We were sitting in a jacuzzi,\nand he said, \"Dad, why do we exist?\""},{"time":1239056,"text":"There is no other question."},{"time":1240620,"text":"Nobody has any other question."},{"time":1242134,"text":"We have variations of this one question,\nfrom three onwards."},{"time":1246123,"text":"So when you spend time in a company,\nin a bureaucracy, in an organization"},{"time":1251519,"text":"and you're saying, boy --"},{"time":1253142,"text":"how many people do you know\nwho on their death beds said,"},{"time":1255859,"text":"boy, I wish I had spent\nmore time at the office?"},{"time":1258264,"text":"So there's a whole thing \nof having the courage now --"},{"time":1263314,"text":"not in a week, not in two months,"},{"time":1265222,"text":"not when you find out \nyou have something --"},{"time":1267516,"text":"to say, no, what am I doing this for?"},{"time":1270388,"text":"Stop everything. Let me do something else."},{"time":1272505,"text":"And it will be okay,"},{"time":1274070,"text":"it will be much better\nthan what you're doing,"},{"time":1276341,"text":"if you're stuck in a process."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1279449,"text":"CA: So that strikes me as a profound\nand quite beautiful way to end"},{"time":1282651,"text":"this penultimate day of TED."},{"time":1284277,"text":"Ricardo Semler, thank you so much."},{"time":1285955,"text":"RS: Thank you so much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1287532,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}